Class Woodwind

  • java.lang.Object
    • Instrument
      • Wind
        • Woodwind
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Clarinet, Flute, Oboe, TenorSaxophone

    abstract class Woodwind
extends Wind
    Woodwind.java represents a woodwind instrument that inherits from Wind, and is a superclass of Flute, TenorSaxophone, Clarinet, and Oboe.
    Since:
    October 20, 2020
    Version:
